=E2=80=94An Australian investor tells the New Yorker (https://www.newyorke=
r.com/magazine/2020/04/20/the-price-of-the-coronavirus-pandemic) he=E2=80=
=99s earning a lot more thanks to predicting the current pandemic.
Charlotte Jee

